title: Ebro In The Morning - Styles P + Havoc Talk New Album "Wreckage Manner"
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Styles P and Havoc join Ebro In The Morning to discuss their new album titled "Wreckage Manner." They reminisce over coming up in the 1990's and talk about being part of iconic rap groups like Mobb Deep and The Lox.
